                <dd>Advanced</dd>
                <dt>Prerequisites</dt>
                <dd>
                  <p>Not provided</p>
                </dd>
                <dt>Topics</dt>
                <dd>Accessible mobile design and development; Mobile web accessibility guidelines and standards; Testing with screen reader users on mobile devices</dd>
                <dt>WAI Curricula on Web Accessibility</dt>
                <dd>
                  <p>Not provided
