<aside class="box" id="Accessibility Testing"><header class="box-h "> <a href="https://course.com">Accessibility Testing<svg focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-external-link "><use xlink:href="/wai-course-list/assets/images/icons.svg#icon-external-link"></use></svg></a> by Accessible University</header><div class="box-i">
This training provide the baselines of accessibility testing. You will learn how to conduct accessibility evaluations, from using automatic tools to including users with disabilities. This training also provides insights on how to conduct large escale accessibility evaluations and how to better understand accessibility compliance with current standards such as WCAG.
