    <p>Consider: <ul><li>Face-to-face - all teaching sessions are provided on-site</li><li>Online - all teaching sessions are provided online</li><li>Hybrid - teaching sessions are provided simultaneously on-site and online</li><li>Blended - teaching sessions are provided either on-site or online</li></ul></p>
